data.description: Move-in-ready townhome in Southpark!! This immaculate two-story home is in a fabulous location… just a short walk or drive to the RTD Fastracks light rail station at Mineral Avenue & Santa Fe Drive (US-85)! A large Living Room with a vaulted ceiling, 2 skylights and a striking wood-burning fireplace greet you, as you step through the front entry door! The galley Kitchen has been updated with new cabinets, custom-tiled backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances (all included)! The main floor of the Property features a spacious Dining Room, as well as a convenient Half-Bath! Also on the main level, you’ll find lovely bamboo hardwood floors throughout most areas! On the upper level, the Primary Suite includes 2 large closets, and a remodeled Full-Bath with new tile and large soaker tub! There’s also a Loft that would be perfect for a TV Den or a Home Office! The 2nd Bedroom completes the upper level! Be sure to notice the new interior paint throughout, as well as the (very) recently cleaned carpet! Downstairs, the full unfinished Basement (572 sf) was built with 2 large windows, and is ready for your plans and dreams -- perhaps a Family/Media Room, a 3rd Bedroom, an additional Bathroom or ??? This Property also features an oversized, 2-car, attached garage with a new roll-up door, opener, and bright finished walls! Due to one of the hailstorms this past summer, the following work has been completed (resulting all NEW elements!)…  composite asphalt shingle roof, all exterior glazing on the front elevation, gutters, and downspouts! Finally, this Listing is only a short walk to all Southpark community amenities, including the park, playground, tennis court, and swimming pool! Via Santa Fe Drive, you’ll also have quick access to C-470, downtown Denver and nearby retail!  [whew]
